{"aid": "igkovlj75n918c", "error": null, "result": {"default_anonymity": "no", "status": "active", "i_edits": [], "q_edits": [], "bookmarked": 6, "request_instructor": 0, "history": [{"uid": "i6ry1ln7xRU", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-03T06:55:48Z", "content": "<p>   看资料 80386的实模式下PA = cs  * 16 &#43; ds &#xff0c;网上说是1M寻址空间 但是1M = 2^20 我就好奇这1M是怎么算出来的</p>", "subject": "80386 实模式 1M寻址"}], "s_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "tag_good_arr": [], "request_instructor_me": false, "my_favorite": false, "t": 1446634579651, "children": [{"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-03-03T07:50:09Z", "id": "i6szwmksn7h17c", "tag_endorse": [], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-03T07:50:09Z", "content": "<p>所有与x86 CPU相关的问题都可以查阅Intel的Architecture Software Developer&#39;s Manual&#xff08;简称SDM&#xff09;&#xff1a;<a href=\"http://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/processors/architectures-software-developer-manuals.html\">http://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/processors/architectures-software-developer-manuals.html</a>。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>有关实模式的内容&#xff0c;参见第一卷3.3.1节和第三卷20.1节&#xff0c;简而言之&#xff0c;实模式下只支持1M的寻址空间。</p>", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-04T03:41:07Z", "id": "i6u6g88rxx0os", "updated": "2015-03-04T03:41:07Z", "subject": "<p>CS和IP都是16位&#xff0c;CS左移4位&#xff0c;加到一起只有20位。20位二进制数的表示范围就只有2^20&#xff0c;这就是1024*1024&#xff0c;也就是1M.</p>", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 27, "bucket_name": "Week 3/1 - 3/7", "no_upvotes": 0, "children": [], "type": "followup"}, {"uid": "i6um7uuk5ka1z6", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-05T11:06:09Z", "id": "i6w1sdpgvfw469", "updated": "2015-03-05T11:06:09Z", "subject": "<p>根据PA = CS * 16 &#43; IP&#xff0c;实际可以寻址的最大地址应该是CS=0xFFFF并且IP=0xFFFF&#xff0c;这个地址超过了1MB。在80286之前&#xff0c;因为地址总线只有20位&#xff0c;所以&#xff0c;实际访问的地址是PA % 1MB的结果&#xff0c;也就是如果地址计算结果超过1MB&#xff0c;实际访问的内存会绕回到低地址。在80286中&#xff0c;地址总线被扩充到24位。当地址总线扩充之后&#xff0c;一些依靠这种trick的DOS程序会出错&#xff0c;IBM为了保持PC的兼容性&#xff0c;在主板上的A20总线增加了一个门电路&#xff0c;称之为A20 Gate。在开机默认状态下&#xff0c;A20 Gate是关闭的&#xff0c;此时A20地址线始终保持0&#xff0c;保证了向后的兼容性。通过特殊的方法&#xff0c;可以将A20 Gate开启&#xff0c;此时就可以自由访问所有内存。在众多开启A20 Gate的方法中&#xff0c;一种是使用键盘控制器8042的一个未被使用的管脚来当作A20 Gate的控制线&#xff0c;ucore使用的就是这种方法。</p>", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 27, "bucket_name": "Week 3/1 - 3/7", "no_upvotes": 0, "children": [], "type": "followup"}, {"uid": "i7e5cw4xLAU", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-08-03T10:03:36Z", "id": "icvr1kq8n3y5np", "updated": "2015-08-03T10:03:36Z", "subject": "我觉得题主的问的意思是为什么2^20是1M&#xff0c;而不是128KB&#xff0c;你觉得是128KB是这样算的&#xff1a;1024*1024=1048576bit=128KB&#xff0c;而1M是这样算得到的&#xff1a;1024*1024=1048576Byte=1MB。而根本原因就是80386的CPU的存储字长是8bit&#xff0c;即2^20是得到1M的存储单位。每个单位是8bit=1Byte", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "no_upvotes": 0, "children": [{"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "created": "2015-08-03T10:45:49Z", "id": "icvsjvhcta24tn", "updated": "2015-08-03T10:45:49Z", "subject": "<p>2^20就是1M&#xff0c;没有你想的那么复杂。</p>", "anon": "no", "folders": [], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": null}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "children": [], "type": "feedback"}], "type": "followup"}], "type": "question", "unique_views": 165, "created": "2015-03-03T06:55:48Z", "id": "i6sxyqahoex3ex", "no_answer": 0, "nr": 14, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "upvote_ids": [], "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "folders": ["lab1"], "bucket_order": 2, "change_log": [{"uid": "i6ry1ln7xRU", "when": "2015-03-03T06:55:48Z", "data": "i6sxyqakzb43ey", "anon": "no", "type": "create"}, {"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "when": "2015-03-03T07:50:09Z", "data": "i6szwmkvhl417d", "to": "i6sxyqahoex3ex", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "when": "2015-03-04T03:41:07Z", "to": "i6sxyqahoex3ex", "anon": "no", "type": "followup"}, {"uid": "i6um7uuk5ka1z6", "when": "2015-03-05T11:06:09Z", "to": "i6sxyqahoex3ex", "anon": "no", "type": "followup"}, {"uid": "i7e5cw4xLAU", "when": "2015-08-03T10:03:36Z", "to": "i6sxyqahoex3ex", "anon": "no", "type": "followup"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "when": "2015-08-03T10:45:49Z", "to": "i6sxyqahoex3ex", "anon": "no", "type": "feedback"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "tags": ["lab1", "student"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 0, "tag_good": []}}